@startuml
title Sequence 11 - Mengakses File Laporan Akhir
autonumber
actor Mahasiswa
participant "Frontend Portal" as FE
participant "Placement API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Storage\nlocal/S3" as Storage

Mahasiswa -> FE: Buka status laporan
FE -> API: GET /placements/{id}/report
API -> DB: Validasi placement milik mahasiswa
API -> DB: Ambil auto_generated_report_url
alt URL tersedia
  DB --> API: URL laporan
  API --> FE: Report status + URL
  FE -> Storage: Buka URL/presigned URL
  Storage --> FE: File PDF
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Browser membuka laporan
else belum tersedia
  API --> FE: Status belum dibuat
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan belum tersedia
end
@enduml
